@startuml
actor User
participant FlightsController
participant FlightService
participant Route
participant Flight

User -> FlightsController : wybór daty / lotniska
FlightsController -> FlightService : searchFlights(from, to, date)
FlightService -> Route : operatesOn(day)
FlightService -> Flight : create / retrieve
FlightService --> FlightsController : List<Flight>
FlightsController -> User : wyświetlenie lotów
@enduml
